THIRD-PARTY NOTICES

This project bundles or derives data from the following third-party sources,
each under its own license. The MIT license above does not alter their terms.

1. VSOP87 planetary theory (Bretagnon & Francou, Bureau des Longitudes).
   Public-domain astronomical theory. Coefficient tables in
   `saju-core/src/main/resources/io/github/jaeyeonling/saju/astronomy/` carry
   their upstream provenance and license in their file headers
   (commenthol/astronomia, MIT; Sonia Keys, MIT).

2. Golden test vectors in `*/src/test/resources/golden/*.csv` were generated
   by freezing the output of tyme4j (https://github.com/6tail/tyme4j, MIT) at
   check-in time. They are test fixtures only and are not shipped in any
   published artifact.
